welcome_message_body: Welcome to Federal Way, where charm meets natural beauty! Known for its stunning parks, vibrant culture, and family-friendly attractions, we invite you to immerse yourself in all the city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The North Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves mainly Alaska Airlines flights.

terminals.name: South Satellite Terminal
terminals.description: The South Satellite Terminal at Seattle-Tacoma International Airport serves mainly international flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Industrial Airport serves all commercial flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Industrial Airport handles all freight and cargo operations, providing efficient and secure handling of goods.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at McChord AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at McChord AFB Airport is used exclusively for military flights.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but a valid military ID is required for access.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal serves all commercial flights and is equipped with modern amenities for passenger convenience.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: This terminal caters to private and chartered flights, providing a more exclusive and personalized experience for travelers.

wifi.note: Passengers can access the airport's WiFi for free by connecting to the designated network.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport serves both commercial and general aviation flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Boeing Field/King County International Airport is primarily used for general aviation and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Kenmore Air Harbor SPB Airport offers a small waiting area, ticketing counter, and baggage claim.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bremerton Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Bremerton Airport is exclusively for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
